HC_How can I find the mask model?

Krävs

HC_Mask model help

HC_If you don't have the packaging, try looking on the mask itself.

HC_For ResMed masks, you can find the mask model printed on the mask itself, or on the headgear (straps), as shown in the following examples.

HC_Is it AirFit or AirTouch?

HC_The "cushion" is the part of the mask that rests on your face. ResMed AirFit masks have a silicone cushion and AirTouch masks have a foam cushion.
